  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This protocol describes a randomized, two arm clinical trial comparing two topical treatments
      in patients with hypergranulation tissue at gastrostomy tube sites. The subjects are
      randomized to either group 1or group 2 treatments:

      Maximum duration of therapy is 4 weeks. However, the therapy may be discontinued anytime at
      the discretion of the investigator or if there is resolution of the of the hypergranulation
      tissue.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
